author: By James Wilkinson and Liam Quinn For Dailymail.com
description: A private jet flying in to a New Jersey airport crashed on Monday afternoon, causing a terrifying inferno that engulfed multiple buildings, authorities have confirmed.
title: Private jet crashes in New Jersey residential area

author: Daniel Trotta
description: An Afghan-born U.S. citizen accused of planting bombs in New York and New Jersey fired on police in New Jersey to evade arrest, but those crimes fall short of attempted murder as charged, his defense lawyer argued on Monday.
title: Accused bomber Rahimi seeks reduced charges in New Jersey case

author: Daniel Trotta
description: A small plane crashed on its approach to Teterboro Airport in New Jersey on Monday, killing two pilots and sparking fires that could be seen from New York, the Federal Aviation Administration and police said.
title: Learjet crashes on approach to New Jersey airport, killing two pilots

description: The Latest on a jet crash near a New Jersey airport (all times local):
title: The Latest: Police: No injuries on ground in plane crash

author: Lucy Clarke-Billings
description: The Federal Aviation Administration said a Learjet 35 crashed about a quarter of a mile shy of Teterboro Airport in New Jersey
title: Two dead as small plane crashes into residential area near US airport

author: Natalie Evans, Lucy Clarke-Billings
description: Two people were killed when the twin-engine Learjet 35 came down in an industrial area in New Jersey on Monday afternoon
title: CCTV captures horrific moment private jet crashes on approach to airport
